{"id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MzUwNA_0009","text":"情歌 已爲你寫過 只爲你一個","structure":{"line_index":9,"char_count":12},"semantics":{"themes":["專一","愛情","獨特"],"sentiment":"VERY_POSITIVE","keywords":["情歌","寫過","只為你"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,3,5,5,9,4,9,5,3,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["cing4","go1","ji5","nei5","se2","gwo3","zi2","nei5","jat1","go3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"情歌","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"已爲","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"寫","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"過","pos":"PART"},{"text":"只爲","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"一個","pos":"NUM"}],"syntax_notes":"「情歌已為你寫過」和「只為你一個」強調歌曲的專屬性，情感濃厚。"},"source":{"title":"幸運鈴聲","artists":["古巨基"],"lyricists":["陳少琪"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_3504","prev_line_id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MzUwNA_0008","next_line_id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MzUwNA_0010","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MzUwNA_0010","text":"憑什麼可使你明白我","structure":{"line_index":10,"char_count":9},"semantics":{"themes":["疑問","理解","情感"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["憑什麼","明白","我"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,2,3,9,9,5,0,2,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["pang4","sam6","mo1","ho2","si2","nei5","ming4","baak6","ngo5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"憑","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"什麼","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"可使","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"明白","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"}],"syntax_notes":"「憑什麼」帶有疑問的語氣，但並非質疑，而是對對方能否理解自己情感的探問。"},"source":{"title":"幸運鈴聲","artists":["古巨基"],"lyricists":["陳少琪"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_3504","prev_line_id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MzUwNA_0009","next_line_id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MzUwNA_0011","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MzUwNA_0011","text":"寧可 感動你一個","structure":{"line_index":11,"char_count":7},"semantics":{"themes":["付出","感動","愛"],"sentiment":"VERY_POSITIVE","keywords":["寧可","感動","一個"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,9,9,2,5,3,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ning4","ho2","gam2","dung6","nei5","jat1","go3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"寧可","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"感動","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"一個","pos":"NUM"}],"syntax_notes":"「寧可」表達一種選擇和決心，即使只能感動一個人（對方），也甘願。"},"source":{"title":"幸運鈴聲","artists":["古巨基"],"lyricists":["陳少琪"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_3504","prev_line_id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MzUwNA_0010","next_line_id":"lyr_5Y-k5beo5Z-6_MzUwNA_0012","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
